              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              class="list-link-icon"
              ><path
                d="M408-480 252-636q-11-11-11-28t11-28q11-11 28-11t28 11l184 184q6 6 8.5 13t2.5 15q0 8-2.5 15t-8.5 13L308-268q-11 11-28 11t-28-11q-11-11-11-28t11-28l156-156Zm272-240q17 0 28.5 11.5T720-680v400q0 17-11.5 28.5T680-240q-17 0-28.5-11.5T640-280v-400q0-17 11.5-28.5T680-720Z"
              ></path></svg
            >Действия персонажа</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="header-links-item">
          <a href="#" class="header-links-item-link"
            ><svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="list-link-icon"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              ><path
                d="M408-480 252-636q-11-11-11-28t11-28q11-11 28-11t28 11l184 184q6 6 8.5 13t2.5 15q0 8-2.5 15t-8.5 13L308-268q-11 11-28 11t-28-11q-11-11-11-28t11-28l156-156Zm272-240q17 0 28.5 11.5T720-680v400q0 17-11.5 28.5T680-240q-17 0-28.5-11.5T640-280v-400q0-17 11.5-28.5T680-720Z"
              ></path></svg
            >Другое</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="header-links-item">
          <a href="#" class="header-links-item-link"
            ><svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="list-link-icon"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              ><path
                d="M408-480 252-636q-11-11-11-28t11-28q11-11 28-11t28 11l184 184q6 6 8.5 13t2.5 15q0 8-2.5 15t-8.5 13L308-268q-11 11-28 11t-28-11q-11-11-11-28t11-28l156-156Zm272-240q17 0 28.5 11.5T720-680v400q0 17-11.5 28.5T680-240q-17 0-28.5-11.5T640-280v-400q0-17 11.5-28.5T680-720Z"
              ></path></svg
            >Скины</a
          >
        </li>
        <li class="header-links-item">
          <a href="#" class="header-links-item-link"
            ><svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="list-link-icon"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              ><path
                d="M408-480 252-636q-11-11-11-28t11-28q11-11 28-11t28 11l184 184q6 6 8.5 13t2.5 15q0 8-2.5 15t-8.5 13L308-268q-11 11-28 11t-28-11q-11-11-11-28t11-28l156-156Zm272-240q17 0 28.5 11.5T720-680v400q0 17-11.5 28.5T680-240q-17 0-28.5-11.5T640-280v-400q0-17 11.5-28.5T680-720Z"
